Say something.

571
00:42:01,455 --> 00:42:04,541
Who moved the table?

572
00:42:22,393 --> 00:42:25,521
Frankie? Did I wake you?

573
00:42:25,646 --> 00:42:28,023
That's pretty sad music.

574
00:42:28,149 --> 00:42:31,068
Sad? It's a dirge.

575
00:42:31,193 --> 00:42:33,320
I almost won five thousand dollars.

576
00:42:33,446 --> 00:42:35,489
Five thousand?!

577
00:42:35,614 --> 00:42:38,200
Why didn't you quit
when you were ahead?

578
00:42:38,326 --> 00:42:42,955
- Ask me an easier question.
- All right, I will.

